# CODEOWNERS — automatic reviewers for matching paths.
# Owners must be GitHub users/teams with write access. Rules are last-match-wins.
#
# TODO: replace the placeholder owners below with real GitHub handles/teams.
#   - The org team @orchestraplatform/maintainers must exist (repo settings > Teams).
#   - The org team @orchestraplatform/template-reviewers must exist and have write
#     access, or CODEOWNERS review requirements will silently not apply.

# Default owner for everything not matched by a more specific rule below.
# Sean is responsible for the platform (see CLAUDE.md).
*                                               @orchestraplatform/maintainers

# CI/CD and deploy machinery stays with platform maintainers.
/.github/**                                      @orchestraplatform/maintainers
/deploy/**                                       @orchestraplatform/maintainers

# Git-managed workshop templates (ADR-0006). Changes here are curriculum/content
# and get an extra review from the template-reviewers group. Scope covers the
# template YAML, the generated schema, and the shared validation package.
# NOTE: rules are last-match-wins, so these stay *below* the broad /deploy rule
# to keep the templates directory owned by template-reviewers.
/deploy/charts/orchestra/files/templates/**     @orchestraplatform/template-reviewers
/template-tools/**                              @orchestraplatform/template-reviewers
